INTENDED USE DISCLAIMER
-----------------------
This software is developed for authorized defense research, security testing,
educational purposes, and lawful surveillance applications. Users are solely
responsible for ensuring their use of this software complies with all
applicable local, state, national, and international laws and regulations.

DATASET ATTRIBUTION
-------------------
This project utilizes the DroneAudioDataset by Sara Al-Emadi et al.
Repository: https://github.com/saraalemadi/DroneAudioDataset

If using this dataset, please cite:
    Al-Emadi, Sara, et al. "Audio Based Drone Detection and Identification
    using Deep Learning." 2019 15th International Wireless Communications
    & Mobile Computing Conference (IWCMC). IEEE, 2019.

NO WARRANTY FOR CRITICAL APPLICATIONS
-------------------------------------
This software is provided for research and development purposes. It has NOT
been validated for deployment in life-critical or safety-critical systems.
The authors make no guarantees regarding detection accuracy, false positive
rates, or false negative rates in production environments.

Users deploying this system for actual security applications must conduct
their own validation, testing, and certification appropriate to their
specific use case and regulatory requirements.
